# Gmail Configuration for SOS Emergency Emails
# IMPORTANT: Use an APP PASSWORD, NOT your regular Gmail password!
#
# SETUP STEPS:
# 1. Go to myaccount.google.com
# 2. Click "Security" in left menu
# 3. Enable "2-Step Verification" (if not already)
# 4. Go back to Security > App passwords
# 5. Select Mail > Windows Computer
# 6. Copy the 16-character password shown
# 7. Paste below (keep spaces as-is)
#
# IF EMAIL FAILS:
# - Verify 2FA is enabled
# - Try generating a NEW App Password
# - Wait a few minutes before trying again
# - Make sure this file is saved

